text: Surface symptoms. Deep problem is the emergence of a techno-industrial super-organism, in which critical functions are totally concentrated within specialized productive organ, typically hosted by some nation that knows how to game liberal trade theory.
Much more serious threat to robust acceleration is cooption and smothering within a fragile global superorganism.
